{
  "stem": "15768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I swept out stores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember working after hours in a card shop on Fifth Avenue where I replaced the cards that needed to be restocked.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And wherever there was money to be made, there I went to see what I could contribute and what I could save in order to further my education.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I became more informed, I realized that in New York the system was if you wanted to take an academic program in college preparation, there were, of course, the sciences, and the languages, and the math that had to be taken.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then being fully aware that I could never just go to college, that I would have to work my way through, I took secretarial courses as well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Doubled my-- doubled up my program, and learned stenography and typing so that I could have a job, secretarial job, and go to night college was the general idea what I was sort of striving for.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't squeeze it all in because from the age of almost 16, I worked for the New York telephone company on their night shift from 3:00 to 11:00, 3:00 in the afternoon to 11:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wonderful pay.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had no time for lunch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did my classes, took no time for lunch, had a sandwich, jumped on the subway, went downtown to Canal Street, and clocked in at 3 o'clock on my job.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And worked on a long distance board, which was the rest of my interesting education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of all the things that I heard over the wires, the way people talked to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to learn American geography in a flash because there were no computers then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We worked on trunks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We plugged in.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
